1. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a new architecture for inductive learning and logic reasoning, which falls under the domain of AI. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper uses neural networks as function approximators, which is a core concept in machine learning. 
3. cs.CL (Computation and Language) - The paper mentions natural language processing tasks such as question answering, which falls under the domain of CL. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper extensively uses neural networks as a key component of the proposed architecture. 
5. cs.PL (Programming Languages) - The paper uses logic programming as a symbolic processor, which falls under the domain of PL.
